PEACEFUL ROBOT REQUIREMENTS FOR 20150509
Version 0.0.1-alpha


PURPOSE AND SCOPE, BUSINESS AND TECHNICAL PERSPECTIVES

Peaceful Robot is a not-for-profit cybersecurity
service that analyze source code, applications and
systems for security weaknesses. Service source code is
open source. Expected funding will be via hosted
service and microdonations.

